{"tid":917453,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【平過5年前】尚城「蝕本價」出貨 呎價跌穿九千","createTime":"2018-11-26T12:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T06:31:11.000Z","uid":147097,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"79b525f24773d7ce553402bccfef0c017761c7b5","tid":917453,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"代理表示，尚城單號洋房，實用面積1,576方呎，剛以1,388萬元易手，呎價僅8,807元，創屋苑洋房項目呎價今年新低。賣方2013年5月向長實(1113)以1,478.4萬元買入單位，至今年6月放盤，原叫價1,780萬元。直至近期，減價至1,490萬元仍無人問津，最終累減392萬元以「蝕本價」出貨。持貨5年賬面貶值6.1%或90萬元，若計金佣金及釐印費等開支，料損手近160萬元。"},{"pid":"2288a708504c410d9a0282e077a6204708d512db","tid":917453,"uid":33907,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"唔....總之乜都唔計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03a5af4c324da5931b171d9469b786a48d9a945","tid":917453,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3zero 同青山道咁撚多錢做乜唔接貨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060ab90df653ace79912ad33c44fdeb703482d1f","tid":917453,"uid":156121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"爽"},{"pid":"ec524aa3292205844ee440cd102b7bc094339f12","tid":917453,"uid":52003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"第一滴血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db01ff341260107df12db3384dcc5ca892f8f958","tid":917453,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢5年實無租過出去啦"},{"pid":"d845265065af344ddfc893abb25a01cc5f86d4ca","tid":917453,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor